---
title: Spinach and Golden Cheese Curry with fresh chilli and cooling coconut milk
description: Spinach is the star of this vibrant curry dish which also features fluffy rice and fresh chillies. Cheese is fried for a crispy and golden finish to make a curry that's too good not to try.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R07_W30_IE_IEVCLV14137-4_Main_high-a10f7aca.jpg
